WEBVTT

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:15.000
The Secret of Gwigok Mountain Lodge

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:18.000
Now I finally feel alive.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:20.000
I was really hungry, chu~

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:25.000
We've been walking around constantly since morning, areum.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:34.000
Where in the world could the other three Princess Teeniepings be, ponni?

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:35.000
Huh?

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:39.000
Graceping, you still haven't eaten?

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:44.000
While she's reading a mystery novel, she won't hear a word we say, ponni.

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:52.000
Lately, Graceping has been so immersed in that, she hasn't even been sleeping properly, areum.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:57.000
Sigh... Mystery novels are really fun, sappun.

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:00.000
If you're done reading, hurry up and eat.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:04.000
I'm full even without eating, sappun.

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:08.000
She really is completely hooked, chu~

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:11.000
Ah! Rain...!

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:19.000
Where did this rain come from all of a sudden?

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:22.000
Why isn't there a path going down?

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:25.000
I can't see well because of the rain, areum.

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:28.000
It looks dangerous to go any further.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:31.000
Brrr... I'm getting a bit cold too...

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:37.000
Guys, there's something over there, chu!

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:45.000
Let's hurry and go see, ponni!

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:51.000
This place is... exactly like a crime scene from a mystery novel...!

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:57.000
Let's get out of the rain first.

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:03.000
Excuse me~ Is anyone here?

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:06.000
The door is open, ponni?

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:09.000
I sense the smell of a mystery in there, sappun...!

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:13.000
You can't just go in like that!

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:20.000
Um... Hello? I'm sorry for intruding so suddenly.

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:29.000
Kyaaak!

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:32.000
Is there no one here?

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:36.000
It looks like it's been empty for a long time, chu.

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:41.000
It's a bit spooky somehow...

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:48.000
Let's rest over there, ponni.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:54.000
I'm getting a hunch about a mysterious case, sappun.

00:03:54.000 --> 00:04:01.000
Thankfully the lights turn on.

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:06.000
Sigh, the rain just won't stop.

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:12.000
Sitting still makes it feel like time is passing even slower, ponni.

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:18.000
It would be nice if there was something to play with, areum...

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:25.000
Ah! I just thought of something.

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:28.000
When did you bring that?

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:36.000
Eight... Nine... Ten! Ready or not, here I come, ponni!

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:39.000
Is it this way?

00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:50.000
Or this way?

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:53.000
Ponni!

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:58.000
Hehe... Could she be this way?

00:04:58.000 --> 00:05:00.000
She's right here...

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:12.000
Gotcha!

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:18.000
Ponni! I'm caught, chu...

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:43.000
Hehe... You're on the second floor, ponni?

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:45.000
Whoa! What is that?

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:49.000
Romi! What's wrong?

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:56.000
What's going on, chu?

00:05:56.000 --> 00:06:03.000
A mystery case... sappun...

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:07.000
Those two in their childhood...

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:12.000
Dianaping, why are you getting along so well with Eclipseping, ponni?

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:18.000
They look like they're having fun, areum.

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:22.000
Huh? Where is Eclipseping going?

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:29.000
I have a bad feeling about this, areum.

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:33.000
The mirror broke, chu!

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:38.000
That... this is...

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:41.000
This is none other than...

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:46.000
Proof that a massive mystery is hidden in this place, sappun.

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:50.000
I will definitely uncover that secret, sappun.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:55.000
There must be a clue somewhere around here... sappun!

00:06:55.000 --> 00:06:58.000
She's starting again?

00:06:58.000 --> 00:07:03.000
She's completely and utterly obsessed, ponni...

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:07.000
Guys, I'm hungry, areum...

00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:11.000
Come to think of it, we haven't had dinner yet.

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:14.000
Graceping, let's look for that later and eat first.

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:19.000
Sappun~

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:23.000
Huh? Why are there only three sandwiches?

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:25.000
Did you guys eat one by any chance?

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:27.000
No.

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:29.000
Huh? That's weird.

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:32.000
I smell a mystery, sappun.

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:35.000
In this case, the culprit is...

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:55.000
Waaaah! What is that?

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:57.000
Aaaaaah!

00:07:57.000 --> 00:08:02.000
Sappun!

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:04.000
Gasp! The window...

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:08.000
It shattered all of a sudden, areum.

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:11.000
Is there really something mysterious going on, chu?

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:17.000
The wind probably just blew hard and a rock flew in from outside, ponni.

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:23.000
No! If something flew in from outside and broke the window, the glass shards should be inside.

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:30.000
But look here. The glass shards have all fallen outside the cabin, sappun.

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:32.000
That means...

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:34.000
That means!

00:08:34.000 --> 00:08:39.000
The culprit is right here inside, sappun!

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:41.000
Uh...!

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:45.000
Hey! Don't scare us! There's no way something like that is...

00:08:45.000 --> 00:08:48.000
Kyaaak! Something just touched me, ponni!

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:52.000
The truth of the mystery is over there, sappun!

00:08:52.000 --> 00:09:00.000
I'm scared...

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:05.000
Wait a minute. It's dangerous.

00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:09.000
Why is the picnic mat here...

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:12.000
The mat was probably originally here...

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:22.000
Gasp!

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:28.000
Take this!

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:32.000
What is this?

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:37.000
Ouch, seeing stars...

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:43.000
Spare us, charle... Ugh, whatever, croak...

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:49.000
Why are you guys coming out of there, chu?

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:53.000
So this was all you guys trying to steal the sandwiches?

00:09:53.000 --> 00:10:01.000
Steal them! We were following you and got so tired... we just took a little...

00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:06.000
It's unfair! We were just trying to secretly protect you, charle!

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:10.000
Because you don't like it when we follow you around, charle...

00:10:10.000 --> 00:10:14.000
Then why did you break the window?

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:18.000
Croak, croak, croak!

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:31.000
According to Croakping, he snuck out alone and was watching from behind the pillar...

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:38.000
He got startled by the thunder and looked back, and there was something outside the window!

00:10:38.000 --> 00:10:46.000
So he threw a rock to chase it away, and it disappeared in an instant, treu.

00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:50.000
I thought it was a ghost, you startled me!

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:56.000
To think the mystery of this cabin was just you guys... sappun.

00:10:56.000 --> 00:11:00.000
Anyway, from now on, tell us before you follow us around, okay?

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:04.000
Ah!

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:09.000
Finally, the real thing! Sappun!

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:11.000
Take this!

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:28.000
I'll yield everything to you, charle!

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:34.000
The thing that was behind the window earlier...

00:11:34.000 --> 00:12:00.000
Then...

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:05.000
Thankfully the rain has stopped and the weather has cleared up.

00:12:05.000 --> 00:12:11.000
Still, I'm glad we got to eat the leftover sandwiches, chu~

00:12:11.000 --> 00:12:14.000
I'm glad we can go back home safely, areum.

00:12:14.000 --> 00:12:17.000
It's a relief nothing bad happened, ponni.

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:22.000
My mystery is over, sappun...

00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:28.000
What in the world was that thing the Magic Mirror showed us yesterday, ponni?

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:31.000
Who cares.

00:12:31.000 --> 00:12:32.000
It's just good we're going back safely.